Fixed problem with the collision detection
Don't actually need the build directory anymore...

Removed a bit of level text I didn't like too much
Added an image to the readme
Added another screenshot to the readme
Added more information to the readme
Added a function that resets all the doors
Created a generator to get all the keypads
Added a reset function for keypads
Progress bars are added back into the entities group
Player dies when health is less than 0
Reordered saves.py to make it more readable
Started on allowing to save progress by making save_data allow more than controls
